title: Tied For Tickling--------TFT - Jan 15, 2012 - Diana Prince
description:
TIED FOR TICKLING\TFT - Jan 15, 2012 - Diana Prince   + Pics



Diana's an easy and sensitive subject. She immediately goes into sensory overload the moment that Bane touches her. Her shrieks fill the air and her pleas go unheard...She gets a brief breather as her flesh is soothed and then the next tickling blitz starts again. Attention is shifted to her soles and toes before a final frenzy is launched
